    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver a linear power band, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate chassis fatigue and a full VANOS bulletproofing. The drivetrain remains tight, featuring a functional M-variable differential lock and a suspension refreshed with Bilstein dampers for maintained turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and age-appropriate patina, the internal mechanical tolerances are within spec, offering a visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
