    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2015 Porsche Cayman that perfectly balances performance and daily usability. The exterior is finished in a deep Basalt Black Metallic that retains a brilliant luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with spirited weekend drives, the body panels are straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Inside, the black leather interior remains supple and clean. You will find very light surface creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the cabin remains free of smoke or pet odors, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is turn-key. It has been serviced strictly at 10,000-mile intervals, with a recent brake fluid flush and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires installed less than 2,000 miles ago. The 2.7L flat-six engine pulls smoothly through the rev range, and the PDK transmission delivers crisp, immediate shifts. It comes with a complete set of service records, two keys, and the original owner's manual. This is a solid, honest example of a modern classic that is ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
